## Conventions

- Backend returns `{code, msg, data}` — `code` is inconsistent (`"0"` / `"200"` / `"201"` / int `0`). Use `ResponseEnvelope` helpers.
- Backend Chinese error messages → map to English via `BackendErrorMessages` before surfacing.
- Every repository method returns `Either<Failure, T>`. No throws escape repos.
- All user-facing strings go through `AppStrings` + `_K` keys (en / zh / es). Do not hardcode English.
- `if (mounted)` before `setState` after async in StatefulWidget.
- `useRootNavigator: true` on any `showDialog` / `showModalBottomSheet`.
- No hardcoded `Colors.white` / `Colors.black` — use `AppColors` or theme.
- Prefer `const` constructors aggressively (we lint for it).

