## Dev workflow

```bash
# Run on Chrome for fast iteration
flutter run -d chrome --web-port 3003

# Run iOS simulator
flutter run -d "iPhone 15"

# Regenerate freezed / json_serializable
dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs

# Lint
flutter analyze

# Sandbox gotcha: build_runner needs full permissions to touch the Flutter engine stamp
```

## After every meaningful change (non-negotiable)
1. `flutter analyze` — must be clean
2. `git add -A && git commit -m "..." && git push origin main`
3. `rsync -av --exclude='node_modules' --exclude='.git' --exclude='build' --exclude='.dart_tool' ~/Development/EvairSIM-App/ ~/Library/Mobile\ Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/EvairSIM-App-Backup/`
4. Update `docs/CONVERSATION_HISTORY.md` when a feature / decision / pivot happens.

